document_data.caption: A map showing Alex Lenter's Storage outlined in red.
document_data.name: Alex Lenter's Storage
document_data.mainbody: '''Alex Lenter's Storage''' was a warehouse located in [[Waterdeep]] during the mid-to-late 14{{th}} century [[DR]].
document_data.Description: The building stood two stories tall.
document_data.Location: Alex Lenter's Storage was located in the central section of the [[Waterdeep/Dock Ward|Dock Ward]] on the southwest side of the intersection of [[Trollcrook Alley]] and [[Zastrow Street]].
